# Bebe AI Studio - Environment Configuration
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# IMPORTANT: Add your OpenAI API Key here
# Get it from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Optional: Set the model (default is gpt-4o-mini)
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 
# 1. Go to https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# 2. Create a new API key or copy an existing one
# 3. Replace "your_openai_api_key_here" with your actual key
# 4. Save this file
# 5. Restart your development server (npm run dev)
# 
# 6. Test the chat at: https://v0-bebe-ai-studio.vercel.app/studio
# 
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RATE LIMITS & PRICING:
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# gpt-4o-mini: ~$0.00015 per 1K input tokens, $0.0006 per 1K output
# Set API budget limits at: https://platform.openai.com/account/billing/limits
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
